{"tid":1090332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豐田免費開放電動車逾2.3萬項專利","createTime":"2019-04-03T11:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T12:49:58.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4b44d59884116e303c9e0d191cf0f9a0394ad2d4","tid":1090332,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/04/03/2101997_39eb028128de9ef2917eddbd9affffc8_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F04%2F03%2F2101997_39eb028128de9ef2917eddbd9affffc8_320.jpg&h=6cdb34d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本汽車製造商豐田(Toyota)宣布，將免費開放混合動力車(HV)等電動車相關技術的逾2.3萬項專利，期望藉此推動其他企業引進豐田技術以擴大市場。<br />\n<br />\n豐田副社長寺師茂樹表示，全球環保規定要求逐年提升，加強了與其他公司合作的想法。<br />\n<br />\n豐田是次將免費開放的專利多達23740項，涉及引擎、電池等核心零部件<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2101997/%E8%B1%90%E7%94%B0%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%BE2.3%E8%90%AC%E9%A0%85%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2101997%2F%25E8%25B1%2590%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2580%25BE2.3%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%25A0%2585%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2588%25A9&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5B5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=0c427337\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2101997/%E8%B1%90%E7%94%B0%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%BE2.3%E8%90%AC%E9%A0%85%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9</a>"},{"pid":"a3dadb5e2e143d532de49dac86d2b0610e47b9a3","tid":1090332,"uid":20241,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那搶左轉頭改個名改個圖去註冊<br />\n豐田真係玩撚死自己"},{"pid":"bc8fc071512d7d85ab58db1b4f6ac003